{"tid":1267460,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何韻詩紅地毯轟港府不仁 Eason台灣金曲獎心繫盧凱彤","createTime":"2019-06-30T01:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T02:15:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2af2689b4ea5a7db4d6dd803f340af4b6e959a7f","tid":1267460,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T01:30:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190630/20716561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F20716561&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=a617f3dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190630%2F20716561&h=f22bde21\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190630/20716561</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩紅地毯轟港府不仁<br />\nEason台灣金曲獎心繫盧凱彤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190630/large/30ec3p10e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190630%2Flarge%2F30ec3p10e.jpg&h=d29b96d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nEason昨晚出席金曲獎，行紅地毯時提及已故戰友盧凱彤（小圖）。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n第30屆金曲獎頒獎典禮昨晚在台北小巨蛋舉行，陳奕迅（Eason）獲入圍提名兼擔任開場演出嘉賓，他穿上皮褸戴超行紅地毯，成功搶風頭，更引來現場觀眾尖叫。被問及參加金曲獎心情？他笑說：「還是很興奮，可能是你們的熱情。」由於打頭陣表演，他透露在意自己的演出水準，所以之前不斷練習。對於身兼表演者及頒獎人，他表示心情緊張：「怕頒獎會說錯話，比較緊張，怕會超時。」他又表示專輯獎是整體性，因很多人一起參與，而且盧凱彤也在其中。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚另一焦點是林志玲舊愛、留了鬍鬚的言承旭，他事前已透過經理人表示行紅地毯時不拍照、不受訪，似是避談林志玲閃婚。雖然言承旭講明不受訪，但路過採訪區時，被問及林志玲結婚是否祝福對方，他一臉尷尬快步離開，以苦笑回應記者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190630/large/30ec3p12e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190630%2Flarge%2F30ec3p12e.jpg&h=fc6dbe52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n言承旭出席金曲獎時，避談舊愛林志玲閃婚。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190630/large/30ec3p13newe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190630%2Flarge%2F30ec3p13newe.jpg&h=30105e1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧紫棋昨晚演唱十首發燒金曲。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190630/large/30ec3p11e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190630%2Flarge%2F30ec3p11e.jpg&h=c5e08297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何韻詩以黑衣配黃色外套現身台灣金曲獎紅地毯。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n言承旭尷尬苦笑<br />\n<br />\n同場的何韻詩以一身黑衣配黃色外套現身，並說：「我作為香港歌手，應該把這個帶來，自從雨傘革命開始，一直有在比較前線給學生支持，這次比起雨傘革命，我覺得更大，民眾的不滿還有牽涉的範圍又更大，作為成年人，也不忍學生們在街上，三個多禮拜了，一個不仁的政府，不聽不聞不理他們的訴求，他們抗爭多久，我就會跟着他們多久。」<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩續說：「香港政府還是用非常敷衍的方法來回應，昨天我們的特首說她決定不會下台，我們需要做的，就是把抗爭延續下去，你們的選舉在明年，你們應該要更站出來投票，守住自己的地方，守住自己的家。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鄧紫棋百萬行頭<br />\n<br />\n另一表演嘉賓鄧紫棋穿上黑裙襯百萬珠寶，並於頒獎禮上演唱十首YouTube點擊破億的金曲。演奏類最佳專輯《Lines &amp; Stains》的得主「東京中央線」在致辭時興奮大叫：「Taiwan is a great country.」引起台下騷動。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：祖李  <br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n朱千雪婚禮從簡"},{"pid":"5f8bcf59223da187a5832b0915c46bd25a71554a","tid":1267460,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T01:33:38.000Z","msg":"Taiwan is a great country<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宇宙漿仲洗返大陸做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65487bf3ba2e7d6d3fabc91da9196380e39ff6aa","tid":1267460,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f8bcf59223da187a5832b0915c46bd25a71554a","tid":1267460,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T01:33:38.000Z","msg":"Taiwan is a great country<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宇宙漿仲洗返大陸做嘢<img 